Traffic,Live,is,an,online,platform,for,managing,creative,studios,and,projects,Traffic,Live,has,features,for,staff,management,resource,management,and,time,tracking,for,creative,projects,The,Traffic,Live,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Traffic,Live,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,employee,information,accessing,department,information,and,managing,jobs